{
  "texts": [
    "Personal innovators are willing to take risks and embrace failure as an opportunity to learn and grow.",
    "Instructors should create a safe and supportive environment that encourages learners to take risks and learn from their failures.",
    "This will help learners develop a growth mindset and become more resilient.",
    "Importantly, PCR acts as a key inhibitor of PU and BI in terms of the metaverse.",
    "Therefore, it is imperative that strict regulations policies and rules be established and implemented in metaverse-based learning platforms."
  ]
